{"tid":1147324,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"男士香水求教,新手上路","createTime":"2019-05-09T20:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T00:04:12.000Z","uid":230151,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80cab8d42219bd272a0db65d4e8727f1238c6a55","tid":1147324,"uid":230151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T20:34:14.000Z","msg":"爬哂真男人個幾個po,都唔係好搵到自己想要既info先開個新po.<br />\n小弟爬完po知道香水要分季節同場合.想大家推介兩枝香水,一枝春夏(清新)一枝秋冬(文青,比人溫䁔啲既感覺).以下係小弟做過小小research之後準備去試既香水:<br />\n春夏:<br />\nJo Malone wood sage and sea salt(我唔知係唔係公廁)<br />\nVersace Man eau fraiche<br />\n秋冬:<br />\nBurberry London<br />\nTerre d&rsquo;Hermes<br />\n好似四季都ok(?):<br />\nChannel Allure Homme edition blanche <br />\n<br />\n由於小弟唔太鍾意公廁野,所以未到完全冇idea既時候都唔想考慮sauvage 同bleu..<br />\n同埋我夏天係會出極多汗..係咪就算噴清新啲既香水都冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求各位巴絲打指教"},{"pid":"a9efe2694cdb8819801eb5c0c7e1f9b473671a2d","tid":1147324,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"CK One"},{"pid":"cd9308091dc8bf9b4c4fca876055d67ff2bfd585","tid":1147324,"uid":230151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9efe2694cdb8819801eb5c0c7e1f9b473671a2d","tid":1147324,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"CK One"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"本身有諗過,爬完po之後好多人話太淡香完全聞唔到"},{"pid":"ee3ad3239d2eeabb4f6ff712fa4609d6adf9c0ab","tid":1147324,"uid":44600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9efe2694cdb8819801eb5c0c7e1f9b473671a2d","tid":1147324,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"CK One"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:29:07.000Z","msg":"Ck 啲香水散得好快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用開ARMANI"},{"pid":"a584c833da3e4cd6cfd77dd4ecc829ac182ca28f","tid":1147324,"uid":230151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":